race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Mdn Plate
race.comment: CEEKAY'S CHOICE (5) has been knocking on the door of a maiden victory placing in five of seven overall and this is not an overly strong affair. Ready to peak now third-up and only needs some luck navigating from the sticky alley to be playing a major role in the outcome. Former SA galloper OUTDOOR CAT (7) just missed the placings when having her first local outing and will have come on with that run now under her belt. Can make her presence felt. WORLDY SPIRIT (10) resumes here but showed enough when last in work to warrant consideration in a race like this. Keep safe while fresh. PFEIFFER'S KISS (12) managed to hit the frame here on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that day at the races. Include in calculations. UPSTART LOVER (8) best of the rest.
